3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the use of genetic algorithms in artificial intelligence and machine learning, which falls under the scope of AI. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of genetic algorithms in machine learning, which falls under the scope of ML. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the history and development of schema theory, which is relevant to the field of software engineering as it involves the design and implementation of algorithms.
